that matter,

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:34.400
that have the ability to,
you know, adopt these standards.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:36.901
Then they can essentially run
the same applications

00:03:36.901 --> 00:03:38.701
and the same technology.

00:03:38.701 --> 00:03:40.901
So this guy's much happier.

